    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨称德国将“在必要时”支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/scholz-says-germany-to-support-ukraine-as-long-as-necessary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，德国对乌克兰的支持不会减少，他试图缓解人们对执政联盟内部预算紧缩将导致停止向这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家提供资金的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/scholz-says-germany-to-support-ukraine-as-long-as-necessary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:17:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士企业获得更多时间享受俄罗斯禁令豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/swiss-firms-get-more-time-for-exemptions-from-russia-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于许多西方公司不顾国际制裁，仍在俄罗斯继续开展业务，瑞士正给予企业更多时间申请豁免在俄罗斯经营的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/swiss-firms-get-more-time-for-exemptions-from-russia-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:53:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭妮·普利兹克将哈里斯白宫视为美国企业的盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/penny-pritzker-sees-harris-white-house-as-corporate-america-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭妮·普利兹克预测，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯如果当选总统，将与美国企业合作，这对近年来一直难以在民主党内找到盟友的科技、能源和金融行业来说是一个潜在的福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/penny-pritzker-sees-harris-white-house-as-corporate-america-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬支持的迈阿密戴德民主党市长赢得连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/griffin-backed-democratic-mayor-of-miami-dade-wins-reelection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密戴德县民主党市长丹妮拉·莱文·卡瓦于周二顺利获得连任，并在肯·格里芬等亿万富翁的支持下轻松获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/griffin-backed-democratic-mayor-of-miami-dade-wins-reelection</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:46:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷将加入美国集团以促进金属投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院官员表示，阿根廷正在加入美国主导的一项旨在吸引更多关键矿产开采投资的倡议，这是建立不涉及中国的金属供应链的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
